As a 26 Mage now, I used to and still is grouping in HK with the others.  Usually in the guard room.  Believe it or not, I'm actually quite enjoy to be chase by the mob.  Why?  Because it means that we are able to deal out DMG more then the other classes.  <br>
<br>
How I did it?  First of course, have my pet out, buff it, fire shield it.  Charge the pet into melee, then cast the rain set of the spell, this will last three ticks, on the second hit I'll hit with the most powerful blade spell and finally round up with the most powerful bolt spell.  After this, unless you are grouping with someone higher level then you, otherwise I guarrantee the mob will be after your ass!<br>
<br>
Good hunting!<br>
